          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">The two </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Parts</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> rotate relative to each other, with the </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Pin-Joint</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> their center-of-rotation.</text></para>
