          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">There are two </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Symbols" styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Symbols</link><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> for a </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Pin-Joint</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-weight:bold; font-style:italic;" translate="true">:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><image src="Red-14-1b.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-size:6pt; vertical-align:sub;"></image><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> a </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Circle</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">, slightly larger than a </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Point</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">a &apos;Dowel&apos; Symbol when fixed to the </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Base-Part.</text></para>
